Package: sparseVector
Title: Efficient Sparse Numeric Vector Implementation
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Nicholas", "Nasser", , "nan823@utexas.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides an S4 class for representing sparse numeric vectors
    efficiently by storing only non-zero values and their positions. Includes
    methods for common vector operations including arithmetic, statistical
    functions, and transformations that maintain sparsity where possible.
